{"tid":2092283,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"杜加里語出驚人：美斯「半自閉」 唔知基沙文驚乜？！","createTime":"2020-07-03T06:48:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T08:08:57.000Z","uid":72497,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0d54b5dc6e6b4560bcf1f4ddae97305d01a55445","tid":2092283,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:48:51.000Z","msg":"48歲的杜加里在RMC Sport表示：「基沙文怕甚麼呢？一個才1.5米高及半自閉的小朋友？他有時需要成熟一點。我說了一整年了，他跟美斯有問題，他應該要當面與對方對質。是的，美斯應該給予基沙文多點傳球，但老實講我不驚訝。基沙文常失球，又沒有自信。他應該直接跟美斯聊，解決問題。」<br />\n<br />\n杜加里的言論惹來批評，他一度在Twitter寫上為有關美斯的言論道歉，並指自己無意侮辱自閉症的人，但這位1998年世界盃贏家又被指刪除社交媒體回應。此外，他亦有評論到巴塞教頭施迪安，指對方是好人但當教練則不夠果斷，不懂適當地換人。"},{"pid":"377dff3229fbe8397755fd96ac23156aed31447b","tid":2092283,"uid":52939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:51:08.000Z","msg":"1.5米<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59bdcd56a872c4f58c3d6a6eae7aeb55fd6169bc","tid":2092283,"uid":99397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:56:11.000Z","msg":"去巴塞想自己做大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1e22430eef9f79caa1c9277bb41d3bf81b7830","tid":2092283,"uid":20473,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T07:02:39.000Z","msg":"史上最廢既世杯冠軍前鋒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f54d3124f1625e3255ec40ba30e08935ef2d902","tid":2092283,"uid":72497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4b1e22430eef9f79caa1c9277bb41d3bf81b7830","tid":2092283,"uid":20473,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T07:02:39.000Z","msg":"史上最廢既世杯冠軍前鋒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T07:03:18.000Z","msg":"是，55場入8球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed0c60fbeefdeea63791d473a6fecf6f423401da","tid":2092283,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"377dff3229fbe8397755f